<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>CampusMarket</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;}

body{
  background:#f8fafc;
  color:#1e293b;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* NAVBAR */
.navbar{
  position:fixed;
  width:100%;
  top:0;
  padding:20px 8%;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  z-index:100;
  border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;
}

/* LOGO NOVA */
.logo{
  font-size:2rem;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#ff5a1f;
}

.logo span{
  color:#1e293b;
  font-weight:600;
}

.nav-btn{
  background:#ff5a1f;
  border:none;
  padding:10px 20px;
  border-radius:10px;
  cursor:pointer;
  font-weight:600;
  color:white;
}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  padding:120px 8%;
  min-height:100vh;
}

.hero-text{
  max-width:550px;
}

.hero-text h1{
  font-size:3.8rem;
}

.highlight{color:#ff5a1f;}

.hero-text p{
  margin-top:20px;
  color:#475569;
  font-size:1.2rem;
}

.buttons{
  margin-top:30px;
  display:flex;
  gap:15px;
}

.btn{
  padding:14px 25px;
  border-radius:12px;
  border:none;
  cursor:pointer;
  font-weight:600;
  transition:.3s;
}

.primary{background:#ff5a1f;color:white;}
.secondary{background:transparent;border:1px solid #1e293b;color:#1e293b;}

.btn:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);}

/* MOCKUP */
.phone{
  width:260px;
  height:520px;
  border-radius:30px;
  background:black;
  padding:10px;
  box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  animation:float 5s infinite;
}

.screen{
  background:white;
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  border-radius:20px;
  overflow:hidden;
}

.screen img{
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  object-fit:cover;
}

/* COMO FUNCIONA */
.steps{
  padding:120px 8%;
  text-align:center;
}

.steps h2{
  font-size:2.7rem;
  margin-bottom:50px;
}

.step-container{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:30px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.step{
  background:white;
  padding:40px;
  border-radius:20px;
  width:320px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  transition:.3s;
}

.step h3{
  font-size:1.5rem;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

.step p{
  font-size:1.1rem;
  color:#475569;
}

.step:hover{transform:translateY(-10px);}

/* DEPOIMENTOS */
.testimonials{
  padding:120px 8%;
  text-align:center;
}

.testimonials h2{
  font-size:2.7rem;
  margin-bottom:50px;
}

.testimonial-box{
  display:flex;
  gap:30px;
  justify-content:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.testimonial{
  background:white;
  padding:35px;
  border-radius:20px;
  width:340px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.testimonial p{
  font-size:1.1rem;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}

.testimonial strong{
  color:#ff5a1f;
}

/* CTA FINAL */
.cta{
  padding:100px 8%;
  text-align:center;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff5a1f,#ff8c42);
  color:white;
}

.cta h2{
  font-size:2.5rem;
}

.cta button{
  margin-top:20px;
}

/* ANIMAÇÕES */
.reveal{
  opacity:0;
  transform:translateY(40px);
  transition:1s;
}

.reveal.active{
  opacity:1;
  transform:translateY(0);
}

@keyframes float{
  0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}
  50%{transform:translateY(-20px);}
}

/* RESPONSIVO */
@media(max-width:900px){
  .hero{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;}
  .phone{margin-top:40px;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<div class="navbar">
  <div class="logo">Campus<span>Market</span></div>
  <a href="/redirect"><button class="nav-btn">Entrar</button></a>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-text">
  <h1>Transforme fome em <span class="highlight">renda</span></h1>

  <p>
    Descubra lanches incríveis ou comece seu próprio negócio dentro do campus.  
    Simples, rápido e lucrativo.
  </p>

  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="/redirect"><button class="btn primary">Começar agora</button></a>
    <a href="/redirect"><button class="btn secondary">Criar conta</button></a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MOCKUP -->
<div class="phone">
  <div class="screen">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349">
  </div>
</div>

</section>

<!-- COMO FUNCIONA -->
<section class="steps reveal">
  <h2>Como funciona</h2>

  <div class="step-container">

    <div class="step">
      <h3>1. Crie sua conta</h3>
      <p>Leva menos de 1 minuto para começar.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h3>2. Explore ou venda</h3>
      <p>Compre lanches ou comece seu negócio.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h3>3. Ganhe dinheiro</h3>
      <p>Venda para colegas dentro do campus.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- DEPOIMENTOS -->
<section class="testimonials reveal">

  <h2>O que os alunos dizem</h2>

  <div class="testimonial-box">

    <div class="testimonial">
      <p>"Comecei a vender brigadeiro e já faço renda toda semana!"</p>
      <strong>- Dino</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <p>"Muito mais fácil pedir lanche no intervalo."</p>
      <strong>- Rato</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <p>"Melhor ideia dentro do campus!"</p>
      <strong>- Divino</strong>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- CTA FINAL -->
<section class="cta">
  <h2>Comece agora e transforme sua rotina</h2>

  <a href="/redirect">
    <button class="btn primary">Criar conta grátis</button>
  </a>
</section>

<!-- JS ANIMAÇÃO -->
<script>
const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');

window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  reveals.forEach(el => {
    const top = el.getBoundingClientRect().top;
    if(top < window.innerHeight - 100){
      el.classList.add('active');
    }
  });
});
</script>

</body>
</html>